info.name: I can't go - variant 2
info.description: Another variant of the so prolific PrzemyslawZaworski fractal [url]https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4tsyWX[/url]

renderpass.code:
#define mainImage(c,f)                                           \
    c = vec4( ( f+f -(c.xy=iResolution.xy) ) / c.y +2. , 2, 0);  \
    c.x -=  2.;                                                  \
    float t = mod(iTime/8.,2.);                                  \
    for ( int i = 0; i++ < 50; c = vec4(1.2,0,1.4,0) * abs(c) )  \
         c /= dot(c,c), c.z -= .85 + .15* min(t,2.-t)
renderpass.name: Image
